        "Hip_Related": {
          "text": "Acute rheumatic fever\nDevelopmental dysplasia of hip\nFemur fracture\nJuvenile idiopathic arthritis\nLegg-Calve-Perthes disease\nSeptic arthritis of the hip (peds)\nLyme disease\narthritis\nSlipped capital femoral epiphysis\nTransient (toxic) synovitis\nOsteosarcoma",
          "tables": []
        },
        "Other_Causes_of_Limping": {
          "text": "Developmental dysplasia\nFracture\nToddler's fracture\nTillaux fracture\n, adolescent\nNeoplasm:\nLeukemia\nEwings\nOsteogenic sarcoma\nMetastatic\nneuroblastoma\nOsteomyelitis\nMyositis\nOther:\nAppendicitis\nMeningitis\nEpidural abscess (spinal)",
